Torquemada from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-go.info/db/oprog.php?a=Dimwit\">Computer-go.info - Details of Program: Dimwit</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47268\">Suggestions for a sparring partner</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2013</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62056\">C++ code for tuning evaluation function parameters</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 10, 2016</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/alonamaloh/ruy_tune\">alonamaloh / ruy_tune — Bitbucket</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64138\">RuyDos publicly available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2017</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org